 have spent hours researching your topic and you are confident that you are going to win over your boss and hopefully get that well-deserved raise. You begin printing out copies of the presentation for your group when suddenly you notice that your colorful pages begin to come out blank. What could possibly be happening? You check printer carefully and realize that you have run out of ink. Gasping in horror you begin to panic. What are your options? You would completely miss your deadline if you tried to run to the store for more ink. Your presentation is too large to email to the participants. So what do you do? Simply save the presentation on to your memory card and insert it into the printer down the hall that is brimming with ink. You hit the print button and continue to print the presentations. As you breathe a sigh of relief you think to yourself, &#34;Who would have ever thought that a little piece of plastic could save the day?&#34;","For more information on these great little devices and various types of memory card readers please take a look at <a href=\"/card-readers-and-memory-cards-101\">Card Readers and Memory Cards:101</a>. If you have already found the right memory card for your use but are now looking for a memory card reader check out our <a href=\"/best-card-readers\">Card Readers</a>. Now if you need the perfect laptop to add to your media collection, take a look at our <a href=\"/electronics/computers\">Laptop Computers</a>. At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don t Have To. "]},"id":"7a959211-b2e8-4e21-bd1f-163f7410d260","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_5039","url":"/memory-cards-and-printers","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"april-adams","url":"/author/april-adams","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"April Adams","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"ZdPiYUbKxXccV5AQZYi9nD","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-10-13T16:10:22Z","datePubl